name: A/D Changer
desc: You can banish this card from your Graveyard, then target 1 monster on the field; change its battle position.

name: Battle Waltz
desc: Target 1 Synchro Monster you control; Special Summon 1 "Waltz Token" with the current Type, Attribute, Level, ATK and DEF of that monster. Neither player takes any battle damage from attacks involving this Token.

name: Big One Warrior
desc: During your Main Phase, you can send 1 Level 1 monster, except this card, from your hand to the Graveyard to Special Summon this card from your hand.

name: Blind Spot Strike
desc: Select 1 face-up Defense Position monster your opponent controls and 1 face-up Attack Position monster you control. The monster you control gains ATK equal to the opponent's monster's DEF, until the End Phase.

name: Boost Warrior
desc: If you control a face-up Tuner monster, you can Special Summon this card from your hand in face-up Defense Position. All Warrior-Type monsters you control gain 300 ATK.

name: Bri Synchron
desc: If this card is sent to the Graveyard as a Synchro Material, until the end of this turn, the Synchro Monster that used this card as a Synchro Material gains 600 ATK, but its effects are negated.

name: Card Breaker
desc: This card cannot be Normal Summoned or Set. This card can only be Special Summoned, in face-up Attack Position, by sending 1 card from your Spell & Trap Card Zone to the Graveyard.

name: Card of Sacrifice
desc: Draw 2 cards, if the combined ATK of all your face-up Attack Position monsters (minimum 2) is less than the ATK of your opponent's face-up monster with the lowest ATK. You cannot Summon or change Battle Position the turn you activate this card.

name: Cards of Consonance
desc: Discard 1 Dragon Tuner with 1000 or less ATK; draw 2 cards.

card_sets.set_name: Saga of Blue-Eyes White Dragon Structure Deck

name: Damage Eater
desc: During your opponent's turn, when your opponent activates a card or effect that would inflict damage, you can remove from play this card in your Graveyard to change that effect so it increases Life Points by the same amount instead.

name: Dash Warrior
desc: If this card attacks, it gains 1200 ATK during the Damage Step only.

name: Desperate Tag
desc: If a face-up Attack Position monster you control is destroyed by battle, during damage calculation, you can reduce the Battle Damage from this battle to 0 and Special Summon 1 Level 4 or lower Warrior-Type monster from your hand at the end of the Damage Step.

name: Double Cyclone
desc: Target 1 Spell/Trap you control and 1 Spell/Trap your opponent controls; destroy them.

card_sets.set_name: Speed Duel GX: Duel Academy Box
Speed Duel: Trials of the Kingdom

name: Dragon Knight Draco-Equiste
desc:
1 Dragon-Type Synchro Monster + 1 Warrior-Type monster
Must first be Fusion Summoned. Once per turn: You can target 1 Dragon-Type Synchro Monster in the Graveyard; banish that target, and if you do, until the End Phase, this card's name becomes that monster's, and replace this effect with that monster's original effects. While this card is in Attack Position, your opponent takes any effect damage you would have taken from their card effects, instead.

name: Drill Synchron
desc: If a Warrior-Type monster you control attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage to your opponent. Once per turn, when you inflict battle damage to your opponent with this effect: You can draw 1 card.

name: Drill Warrior
desc:
"Drill Synchron" + 1 or more non-Tuner monsters
Once per turn, during your Main Phase 1: You can halve this card's ATK, and if you do, it can attack your opponent directly this turn. Once per turn: You can discard 1 card, and if you do, banish this card. During your next Standby Phase: Special Summon this card banished by this effect, then add 1 monster from your Graveyard to your hand.

name: Effect Veiler
desc: During your opponent's Main Phase (Quick Effect): You can send this card from your hand to the GY, then target 1 Effect Monster your opponent controls; negate the effects of that face-up monster your opponent controls, until the end of this turn.

card_sets.set_name: Noble Knights of the Round Table Power-Up Pack

name: Justice Bringer
desc: Once per turn, when a Special Summoned monster your opponent controls activates its effect, you can negate the activation.

name: Majestic Star Dragon
desc:
"Majestic Dragon" + "Stardust Dragon" + 1 non-Tuner monster
During either player's turn, when your opponent activates a card or effect: You can Tribute this card; negate the activation, and if you do, destroy all cards your opponent controls. Once per turn: You can target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; negate its effects until the end of this turn, and you can activate 1 of its effects as this card's effect once this turn. During the End Phase: Target 1 "Stardust Dragon" in your Graveyard; return this card from the field to the Extra Deck, then Special Summon that target.

name: Power Frame
desc: When a face-up monster you control is targeted for an attack by a monster with a higher ATK: Target the attack target; negate that attack, and if you do, equip this card to that target. The equipped monster gains ATK equal to the difference between its ATK and the ATK of its attacker when this card resolves.

card_sets.set_name: Battle Pack 2: War of the Giants
Battle Pack 2: War of the Giants

name: Second Booster
desc: You can Tribute this card to select 1 face-up Attack Position monster you control. The selected monster gains 1500 ATK until the End Phase.

name: Shield Wing
desc: Twice per turn, this card cannot be destroyed by battle.

name: Sonic Chick
desc: Cannot be destroyed by battle with a monster that has 1900 or more ATK.

name: Stardust Xiaolong
desc: When you Synchro Summon "Stardust Dragon", you can Special Summon this card from your Graveyard in face-up Attack Position. Once per turn, if this card would be destroyed by battle, it is not destroyed.

name: Starlight Road
desc: When a card or effect is activated that would destroy 2 or more cards you control: Negate the effect, and if you do, destroy that card, then you can Special Summon 1 "Stardust Dragon" from your Extra Deck.

card_sets.set_name: Premium Gold: Return of the Bling

name: Stronghold Guardian
desc: If a Defense Position monster you control is attacked, you can send this card from your hand to the Graveyard during the Damage Step to have your attacked monster gain 1500 DEF until the End Phase.

name: Synchro Barrier
desc: Tribute 1 Synchro Monster you control. You do not take any damage until the End Phase of the next turn.

name: Synchro Gift
desc: Select 2 face-up monsters you control (1 Synchro Monster and 1 non-Synchro monster). Until the End Phase of this turn, reduce the ATK of the Synchro Monster to 0, and the other monster gains ATK equal to the Synchro Monster's original ATK.

name: Synchro Material
desc: Target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; you can use that monster as Synchro Material this turn, as if you controlled it. You cannot conduct your Battle Phase the turn you activate this card.

name: Variety Comes Out
desc: Return 1 face-up Synchro Monster you control to the Extra Deck to select and Special Summon a Tuner monster(s) from your Graveyard, whose total Levels equal the Level of that Synchro Monster. You cannot Synchro Summon the turn you activate this card.
